col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285363" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285363"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 192px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 96px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 192px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="519" height="23" style="display: none; top: 1px !important; left: 78px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-272690" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p><i>Hey there, SkinTalks readers! Korean skincare is blowing up in the beauty scene, and it's not just for women anymore. Men's skin care is on the rise, with more and more guys getting into the game, thanks to how easy and effective these routines are.</i></p><p><i><br></i></p><p></p><p><i>I</i><i style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">f you are new to skincare or want to improve your routine, this guide will help you learn about Korean skincare. It will also show you how to achieve </i><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(220, 249, 254);"><i style="">healthy, glowing skin</i></span><i style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"> by giving tips about the best skin care for men.</i></p><p><i><br></i></p><p></p><p><i>And girls, if you’re reading this, get your man and share this with him if he needs some skincare education.&nbsp;</i><i style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">His skin will thank us.</i></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285375" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285375" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717424962943" data-id="1717424962943" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285423" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285423" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/7cd18d0e-6c44-497c-b247-f496dc6c6194/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/pexels-tima-miroshnichenko-6763625.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="2000" height="3000" natural-width="2000" natural-height="3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717424966171" data-id="1717424966171" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285344" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285344"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Skincare is not only for women</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285413" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285413"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 192px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 96px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 192px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-282727" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>Pushing the idea that skincare is just for women is one of the biggest myths out there. Guys, using a face scrub won't make you less manly, and moisturizer definitely won't make your skin greasy nor too soft.</p><p><br></p><p>Men's skin has its unique challenges. It's thicker, oilier, and faces more environmental stress from daily shaving and extra sun exposure. Skipping out on proper skin care can result in ingrown hairs, breakouts, early aging, and other skin problems. So, skincare for men isn't just a marketing ploy—it's essential!</p><p><br></p><p>So let's dive into men's skin care routine and the best skin care products for men.</p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285440" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285440"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-498905" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">The Essential Guide to Korean Skincare Simplified</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285331" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285331"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 768px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 384px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 768px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="93" height="28" style="display: none; top: 505px !important; left: 718px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-86582" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>Embracing the renowned 10-step Korean skincare regimen sounds enticing, doesn't it? But let's be real – sometimes, time and budget constraints make it feel like a distant dream.</p><p><br></p><p>We'll share a simplified routine that delivers results without the fuss. If you're ready to dive deeper, the full 10-step guide is also below. Discover how to achieve <span style="background-color: rgb(216, 247, 252);">radiant skin</span> with our simplified approach first. Then, explore the complete routine at your own pace.</p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285337" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285337" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="9+3" data-layout-md="9+3" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285369" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285369"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Double Cleansing</h3><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285433" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285433"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p></p><p>Double cleansing is a two-step skincare process where you first use an oil-based cleanser followed by a water-based cleanser, in other words, a face wash. Even in your simplified skincare routine, the double cleansing method is non-negotiable. Especially when you live in the city! Because of the high levels of pollution that can penetrate into your pores and deep into your skin.</p><p></p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285425" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285425"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Exfoliation</h3><div></div><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285436" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285436"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Male skin is thicker than female skin, which means that male skin <span style="background-color: rgb(216, 247, 252);">produces more oil and sebum</span>. Therefore, it is a must for men to use an <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">exfoliant </span>in their routine. Something with BHA aka Salicylic acid. Salicylic acid dissolves the oiliness and keeps your pores and complexion clean.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285384" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285384"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Hydration</h3><div></div><div></div><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285460" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285460"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Think of your skin as a sponge. Just like a dry sponge struggles to soak up water, dehydrated skin can't absorb skincare products effectively.</p><p><br></p><p>That’s where serums come in. It's like giving your skin a sip of water before using other products. Therefore it's prepared to absorb all the beneficial nutrients.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717424298948" data-id="1717424298948" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285379" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285379" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/f7e109eb-9fbb-4cfa-84ed-4a036f5264d0/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/kaboompics_skincare-aesthetics-macro-textures-and-backgrounds-34069_small.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="1000" height="1500" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1500"></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285406" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-15" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285406" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="15px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285402" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285402"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Sunscreen</h3><div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285370" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285370"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Sunscreen is a product that will protect your skin from sun damage and aging. It will make your skin look hydrated and fresh-looking! We recommend using it not only during summer months but other times as well.&nbsp;<br><br>If you'd like to dive into the full 10-step guide, here it is:</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285326" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285326"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-903389" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">10-step skin care routine for men</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285354" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285354"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 72px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 36px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 72px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-233841" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>You might have heard about the famous 10-step Korean skincare routine, and while it’s effective, it’s not a must for everyone. Your routine can be as simple or as detailed as you want it to be. We'll go through each step together, explaining the purpose and benefits so you can decide what works best for you and your skin!</p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285353" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285353" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm- gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717423611942" data-id="1717423611942" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285417" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285417" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/2baaff97-f2e8-4a29-8ce1-16bdcffb31d8/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/07-Skincare_for_men.webp" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="400" height="600" natural-width="400" natural-height="600"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717423615132" data-id="1717423615132" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285343" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285343"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Oil cleanser</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285461" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285461"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Let's start with face cleansers for men. An oil cleanser removes dirt and excess oil. It melts away excess sebum without leaving any residue behind or drying out your skin. Use oil cleanser nightly, massage into skin for 30 seconds, then rinse with lukewarm water.</p><p><br></p><p>Start with the <a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/beauty-of-joseon-ginseng-cleansing-oil" class="" data-position="1"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);">Ginseng Cleansing Oil</span><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">,</span></a> which not only effectively removes makeup and impurities but also nourishes your skin with its rich antioxidant properties.</p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285334" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285334"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Face wash</h3><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285405" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285405"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>A face wash for men differs from an oil cleanser because it is water-based. It removes water-soluble impurities, such as sweat and dirt, from your skin's surface. You can use this cleanser in your morning routine and evening routine. When using a face wash with your oil cleanser, it will make shaving a lot easier. Use the face wash with water for at least 30 seconds.</p><p><br></p><p>Follow up with the<span style="background-color: rgba(255, 226, 240, 0.99);"><u style=""><strong style=""><a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/products/acne-facial-cleanser" class="" style="" data-position="2">Acne Cleanser</a>&nbsp;</strong></u></span>to target any blemishes and prevent breakouts. This combination ensures your skin is clean, clear, and well-prepared to absorb the benefits of your subsequent skincare products.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285434" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285434"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Exfoliant</h3><div></div><div></div></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285346" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285346"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 360px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 180px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 360px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-500055" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Exfoliation removes dead skin, allowing skincare products to work better. This makes skin look younger, brighter, and healthier.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">To get the best results, <span style="background-color: rgb(216, 247, 252);">exfoliate 2 to 3 times a week</span> on problem areas, based on what your skin needs. Only use it in your evening routine.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285390" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285390" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285351" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285351"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-735651" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Essence/Toner</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285359" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285359"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 360px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 180px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 360px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-500055" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>A toner or essence helps remove excess oil and dirt left behind by your cleanser. These mild cleansers remove dirt, impurities, and oil effectively. This is especially beneficial for men with oily skin as toning helps to prevent clogged pores that can lead to breakouts. Collect a proper amount into your palm and gently press it onto the skin. Use it in your morning and evening routine.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285357" class="gf_row gf_equal-height gf_row-gap-15" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285357" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="9+3" data-layout-md="9+3" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="15px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285412" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285412"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-398977" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Serum</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285445" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285445"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 768px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 384px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 768px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="30" height="23" style="display: none; top: 25px !important; left: 584px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-595859" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">Let's discuss face serums for men. A face serum is the most fun part of your routine. Serums have the highest concentration of active ingredients. They target specific skin concerns you may have.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">This is the point where skincare becomes more specific, and it's crucial to know your goals. Want to reduce large pores? Think about using Niacinamide, AHA, BHA, or PHA. Skincare gets more detailed now, so it's crucial to understand your objectives.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">The&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);"><b style=""><u style=""><a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/products/anua-niacinamide-10-txa-4-serum" class="" data-position="3" style="">Anua Niacinamide 10% + TXA 4% Serum</a></u></b></span>&nbsp;would be a great addition in your routine if you want to focus on reducing large pores.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">Concerned about enlarged pores? Salicylic acid removes oil and maintains clean pores and complexion.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">Keep your skin hydrated by imagining it as a sponge. Dull skin? Vitamin C serum for men can brighten dull skin, providing a more vibrant and youthful appearance.</p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">Wrinkles? Choose a peptide complex or Retinol. Such as the <a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/products/mary-may-6-peptide-complex-serum?variant=39477214871615" class="" style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);" data-position="4"><u style=""><strong style="">MARY & MAY&nbsp;</strong></u><span style="font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;">&nbsp;6 Peptide Seru</span></a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);">m</span>&nbsp;and <span style="font-weight: bold; background-color: rgba(255, 226, 240, 0.93);"><a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/products/some-by-mi-retinol-intense-reactivating-serum" class="" style="" data-position="5">Some by Mi Retinol Intense Reactivating Serum</a>.</span></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);"><br></p><p style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Poppins; text-align: left; color: rgb(35, 35, 35);">Collect a proper amount into the palms and gently press it onto the skin. Use it in your morning and evening routine. From a few times a week to twice a day, depending on the serum and preference.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1706278641131" data-id="1706278641131" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285352" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285352" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc