-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285362" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285362" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://koreanskincare.nl/cdn/shop/files/5e4692399e5bbe79225d774b2c061899_0b6f91a0-52c9-4176-bf9e-075f99a30f19.jpg?v=1708952918" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="800" height="800" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717423991173" data-id="1717423991173" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285457" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285457"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-196050" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Emulsion</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285393" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285393"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 264px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 132px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 264px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-522812" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>If you've never come across emulsions, you're not alone. These light moisturizers are great for men's skin, especially for those in humid climates who don't like heavy creams.</p><p><br></p><p>So, why should you consider adding an emulsion to your daily routine? Well, for starters, they're the perfect solution for men who want to keep their skin moisturized without feeling like they've slathered on a heavy, greasy cream. Plus, their ability to sink deep into the skin means you'll reap the benefits of all those powerhouse ingredients on a whole new level.</p><p><br></p><p>Use it every morning and evening, massaging into the face and neck.</p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285403" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285403" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717425313039" data-id="1717425313039" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285449" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285449"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-957376" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Moisturiser</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285477" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285477"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 847.5px !important; height: 312px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 423.75px 156px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 847.5px !important; height: 312px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-694755" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>When it comes to choosing the <a href="https://koreanskincare.co.uk/collections/moisturisers" class="" style="background-color: rgb(255, 226, 240);">best moisturiser for men</a>, the options are endless. Face creams, gels, and oils, each serving the crucial role of locking in the benefits of your previous skincare steps. But <span style="background-color: rgb(216, 247, 252);">what exactly makes moisturizers so popular?</span></p><p></p><p><br></p><p>Simply put, moisturizers are the heroes of skincare. Their primary job? To keep your skin hydrated and looking plump and radiant, you should create a protective barrier. This barrier will seal in moisture and prevent water loss.</p><p><br></p><p></p><p>Over the years, the world of skincare has seen an explosion of moisturizer options, catering to a diverse range of skin types and concerns. From combating dryness and dehydration to addressing signs of aging, there's a moisturizer out there for everyone.</p><p></p><p><br></p><p>Use it every morning and evening, massaging into the face and neck.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1717425315862" data-id="1717425315862" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285410" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1734000285410" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/634f8b6c-99b1-4437-9414-b02317b19fc7/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/pexels-sabine-meier-818963894-20369242_edit2.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="auto" data-height="auto" title="" width="843" height="843" natural-width="843" natural-height="843"></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1734000285392" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1734000285392" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1706278098343" data-id="1706278098343"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285398" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1734000285398"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 28.0781px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 14.0391px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 31px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-762778" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Sunscreen</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1734000285427" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1734000285427"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 1140px !important; height: 240px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 570px 120px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 1140px !important; height: 240px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-995937" spellcheck="false" data-gram